TestNG Listners
--
1) Create Test case
2) Create a Listener class
3) Create a XML file and include both Testcase and Listener Class

2) Ways to implement listener class

Method1
---------------

class MyListner implements ITestListner {
// Interface
}

class MyListner extends TestListnerAdapter {
// From class
}


From testng .xml file we can fire the Listener class or
Directly add a Line in the cclass if you run the class Directly

@Listeners(Selenium_Java_TestNG_Part4.MyListener.class)



